{
  "stem": "10162.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was-- it was not too cold to-- nevertheless, I didn't-- don't remember suffering from cold or anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it must have been very late spring.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there-- there we were-- we were guarded by the gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hungarian gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were-- they were bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were bad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were bad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These were-- these were boys brought up from-- from the villages who probably volunteered for this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were just the lords over all these people for life and death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, once they called my mother in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to call women in once in a while to the office.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would torture them to tell where they have money hidden, where in-- what they left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was shielded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From me, my mother shielded these things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I know when she came back that she couldn't wear her shoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then somebody said that they beat her-- the sole of her feet with something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was swollen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was nothing hidden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But by then, we had to-- everything was for long time taken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I remember when we had-- all the Jews had to give every gold, you know, every jewelry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, I had the little neck chain with a little medal, you know, a teeny little earring.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everything had to be-- we really had nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had nothing except what we had on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from there, they-- they-- they-- one day they put us in the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because maybe this is-- was the logistics of this being in this brick factory area that was next to the tracks-- some kind of a railroad tracks for shipping us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I've heard-- I've heard-- I talked to other survivors before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's interesting how similar our stories are and how different our stories are, even the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Cattle cars are not for human transportation as is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it's a big difference if you're 40 or 80 or 120.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were 120 in a cattle car, maybe because it was just so-- so-- it was like a last-minute thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like actually, I have to retrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I have to tell you that by the-- by New Year's Eve of 1943 to 1944, my father was home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my parents had a small New Year's party.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, nothing raucous, just a few friends together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a warmish Christmas-- New Year's night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they opened the window at midnight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they sang the Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they said, it was just as-- as a symbol of-- of-- of-- of feeling that victory is at hand.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, we won the war because this was after the Stalingrad battle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and every day, my father heard on the radio that the Americans are planning to the landing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they will be here any minute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They'll be here any minute.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It turned out that this nice present from this German who threw this condensed food did the baby more harm than good because that's the only food we had somehow with us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we kept giving it to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had the terrible diarrhea, dysentery in the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother at one point hung his little clothes on the-- on that window to dry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And somebody pulled it out from outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he didn't even have that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that-- that, I remember, was a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were in the cattle car extremely long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just cannot tell you how long, like two weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, there is no water and no hygiene and no nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And actually, that's when I learned that my young and beautiful little mother is-- is-- what a strong person she is because she was-- she really kept my spirit up.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She never complained and said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The war is almost over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And these people, these are-- these are just not good people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they are ignorant people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But wherever we'll go, Germans are still civilized people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They are in a-- in a war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They are-- they're doing what they have to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But you'll see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We'll get there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We'll-- we'll probably have to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we are strong and young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we'll work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And soon enough, it will be over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And Daddy will be at the gates waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So you know, that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the reason it took such a long time to go to-- we didn't know our destination-- which through Czechoslovakia to go to Auschwitz, Poland, shouldn't have taken that long time-- was that very many times, they just pushed us off to another track.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
